{"__ud_title":"把 OpenClaw 装进U盘，快速部署即插即用","__ud_tags":[],"__ud_update_time":1777420258774,"__ud_create_time":1777420256641,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"指南Zhinan"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"把 OpenClaw 装进U盘，快速部署即插即用"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"使用 dongsheng123132 的项目，一键制作龙虾U盘吧。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"通过 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://github.com/dongsheng123132/u-claw","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}},{"type":"underline"}],"text":"GitHub"},{"type":"text","text":" 的 U-Claw 达成把 OpenClaw 装进u盘里，做成 U 盘可插任意电脑，双击即用，便携虾！"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"两种 U 盘模式"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"便携版 U 盘Linux 启动盘原理"},{"type":"text","text":"在已有系统（Mac/Win/Linux）上运行 U 盘里的脚本从 U 盘启动整个 Linux 系统 + OpenClaw"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"U 盘要求"},{"type":"text","text":"4GB+"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"64GB+ USB 3.0"},{"type":"text","text":"（USB 2.0 太慢不推荐）"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"依赖"},{"type":"text","text":"电脑已有操作系统不依赖任何已装系统"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"适合"},{"type":"text","text":"临时用、公共电脑、演示专用 AI 工作站、无系统裸机"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"下面为该项目的部署教程："}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"快速开始制作便携版-U-盘"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"快速开始：制作便携版 U 盘"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 1. 克隆代码\ngit clone https://github.com/dongsheng123132/u-claw.git\n\n# 2. 补齐大依赖（Node.js + OpenClaw，国内镜像，约 1 分钟）\ncd u-claw/portable && bash setup.sh\n\n# 3. 拷贝到 U 盘\ncp -R portable/ /Volumes/你的U盘/U-Claw/   # Mac\n# 或 Windows 资源管理器直接拖过去"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"完成！"},{"type":"text","text":" 插上 U 盘，双击启动脚本就能用。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"制作-Linux-启动盘"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"制作 Linux 启动盘"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"把整个 Linux 系统 + OpenClaw 刻在 U 盘，开机从 USB 启动直接进入 AI 助手桌面。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"准备："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"64GB+ USB 3.0 U 盘"},{"type":"text","text":"（推荐三星 BAR Plus、闪迪 CZ880 等高速盘）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Linux Mint ISO（"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/linuxmint-cd/stable/","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}},{"type":"underline"}],"text":"清华镜像"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/linuxmint-cd/stable/","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}},{"type":"underline"}],"text":"中科大镜像"},{"type":"text","text":"）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Rufus v4.0+（"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://rufus.ie/zh/","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}},{"type":"underline"}],"text":"rufus.ie"},{"type":"text","text":"）"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"步骤："}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Rufus 刻录 ISO → 开启 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Persistent Storage"},{"type":"text","text":"（8-16GB）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"USB 启动 → 进入 Linux Mint 桌面 → 连网"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"运行安装脚本："}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"curl -O https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dongsheng123132/u-claw/main/portable/setup-linux-usb.sh\nbash setup-linux-usb.sh"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"详细图文教程见 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://u-claw.org/guide.html","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}},{"type":"underline"}],"text":"guide.html → Linux 启动盘模式"},{"type":"text","text":"。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"U-盘功能一览"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"U 盘功能一览"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"功能MacWindowsLinux免安装运行"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Mac-Start.commandWindows-Start.batbash Linux-Start.sh"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"功能菜单"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Mac-Menu.commandWindows-Menu.batbash Linux-Menu.sh"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"安装到电脑"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Mac-Install.commandWindows-Install.batbash Linux-Install.sh"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"首次配置"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Config.htmlConfig.htmlConfig.html"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"U-盘文件结构"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"U 盘文件结构"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"U-Claw/                          ← 整个拷到 U 盘\n├── Mac-Start.command             Mac 免安装运行\n├── Mac-Menu.command              Mac 功能菜单\n├── Mac-Install.command           安装到 Mac\n├── Windows-Start.bat             Windows 免安装运行\n├── Windows-Menu.bat              Windows 功能菜单\n├── Windows-Install.bat           安装到 Windows\n├── Linux-Start.sh                Linux 免安装运行\n├── Linux-Menu.sh                 Linux 功能菜单\n├── Linux-Install.sh              安装到 Linux\n├── setup-linux-usb.sh            Linux 启动盘内安装 OpenClaw\n├── Config.html                   首次配置页面\n├── setup.sh                      补齐依赖（开发者用）\n├── app/                          ← 大依赖（setup.sh 下载，不进 git）\n│   ├── core/                        OpenClaw + QQ 插件\n│   └── runtime/\n│       ├── node-mac-arm64/          Mac Apple Silicon\n│       ├── node-win-x64/           Windows 64-bit\n│       └── node-linux-x64/         Linux x86_64\n└── data/                         ← 用户数据（不进 git）\n    ├── .openclaw/                   配置文件\n    ├── memory/                      AI 记忆\n    └── backups/                     备份"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"桌面安装版Electron-App"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"桌面安装版（Electron App）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"除了 U 盘便携版，还有桌面 App 版本："}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"cd u-claw-app\nbash setup.sh            # 一键安装开发环境（国内镜像）\nnpm run dev              # 开发模式运行\nnpm run build:mac-arm64  # 打包 → release/*.dmg\nnpm run build:win        # 打包 → release/*.exe"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"支持的-AI-模型"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"支持的 AI 模型"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"国产模型（无需翻墙）："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"模型推荐场景"},{"type":"text","text":"DeepSeek编程首选，极便宜Kimi K2.5长文档，256K 上下文通义千问 Qwen免费额度大智谱 GLM学术场景MiniMax语音多模态豆包 Doubao火山引擎"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"国际模型："},{"type":"text","text":" Claude · GPT · Gemini（需翻墙或中转）"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"支持的聊天平台"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"支持的聊天平台"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"平台状态说明"},{"type":"text","text":"QQ✅ 已预装输入 AppID + Secret 即可飞书✅ 内置企业首选Telegram✅ 内置海外推荐WhatsApp✅ 内置Baileys 协议Discord✅ 内置—微信✅ 社区插件iPad 协议"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"国内镜像"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"国内镜像"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"所有脚本默认走国内镜像，无需翻墙："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"资源镜像"},{"type":"text","text":"npm 包"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"registry.npmmirror.com"},{"type":"text","text":"Node.js"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"npmmirror.com/mirrors/node"},{"type":"text","text":"Electron"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"开发--贡献"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"开发 & 贡献"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"git clone https://github.com/dongsheng123132/u-claw.git\ncd u-claw/portable && bash setup.sh\nbash Mac-Start.command   # Mac 测试\nbash Linux-Start.sh      # Linux 测试"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"平台支持："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"平台状态"},{"type":"text","text":"Mac Apple Silicon (M1-M4)✅Linux x86_64✅Linux ARM64✅Windows x64🚧 开发中Mac Intel❌ 暂不支持"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"相关链接"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"相关链接"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://www.u-claw.org/guide.html","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}},{"type":"underline"}],"text":"https://www.u-claw.org/guide.html"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://github.com/dongsheng123132/u-claw","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}},{"type":"underline"}],"text":"https://github.com/dongsheng123132/u-claw"}]}]}